
<Client-side-application>
    0. init npm to get package.json --> $ npm init
    1. install bower --> $ npm install bower -g
    2. init bower to get bower.json --> $ bower init
    3. create .bowerrc to define dependency and then run --> $ bower init
    4. install jquery and toastr by running --> $ bower install jquery --save / $ bower install toastr --save
    5. install angular --> $ bower install angular angular-resource angular-route --save
</Client-side-application>

